00:21:40.270 --> 00:21:41.437 align:middle line:90%
I want to elaborate on that.

00:21:41.437 --> 00:21:43.300 align:middle line:84%
And to become a
vehicle of creation

00:21:43.300 --> 00:21:45.070 align:middle line:90%
and just let it go and trust--

00:21:45.070 --> 00:21:46.910 align:middle line:90%
another important concept.

00:21:46.910 --> 00:21:49.420 align:middle line:84%
What comes out
surprises me constantly.

00:21:49.420 --> 00:21:52.210 align:middle line:84%
So I feel-- and
oftentimes, I'll create

00:21:52.210 --> 00:21:55.515 align:middle line:84%
something that's completely
unprecedented in my field.

00:21:55.515 --> 00:21:57.140 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, where
did that come from?

00:21:57.140 --> 00:21:58.480 align:middle line:90%
And I call that a quantum leap.

00:21:58.480 --> 00:22:01.240 align:middle line:84%
I call it creativity
