00:22:09.127 --> 00:22:10.210 align:middle line:90%
>>RICHTEL: Charles Schulz.

00:22:10.210 --> 00:22:14.490 align:middle line:84%
So years ago, I had a
syndicated comic strip.

00:22:14.490 --> 00:22:18.480 align:middle line:84%
