00:23:04.950 --> 00:23:09.240 align:middle line:84%
Now, the reason I bring up that
story, and I do so in relation

00:23:09.240 --> 00:23:13.260 align:middle line:84%
to the idea that you
had when you heard

00:23:13.260 --> 00:23:16.770 align:middle line:84%
