dating site, was you

00:23:16.770 --> 00:23:23.010 align:middle line:84%
could argue that that
woman gave you the idea.

00:23:23.010 --> 00:23:25.770 align:middle line:84%
But I would say what
the science suggests

00:23:25.770 --> 00:23:30.780 align:middle line:84%
