00:26:47.000 --> 00:26:48.000 align:middle line:90%
- Can we do one of them?

00:26:48.000 --> 00:26:48.440 align:middle line:10%
Can you do--

00:26:48.440 --> 00:26:50.440 align:middle line:10%
- Well, one of the simplest
ones was contributed

00:26:50.440 --> 00:26:54.150 align:middle line:10%
by my dear friend,
Wendy Palmer, who

00:26:54.150 --> 00:26:58.170 align:middle line:10%
was sixth dan aikido
sensei, a musician,

00:26:58.170 --> 00:26:59.605 align:middle line:10%
leadership consultant and--

00:26:59.605 --> 00:27:00.405 align:middle line:10%
- Creative.

00:27:00.405 --> 00:27:06.550 align:middle line:84%
- --an amazingly powerful and
inspirational human being.

00:27:06.550 --> 00:27:08.730 align:middle line:84%
And her generation
phase exercise--

00:27:08.730 --> 00:27:11.188 align:middle line:84%
I asked her, what would you
like to contribute to the book?

00:27:11.188 --> 00:27:13.110 align:middle line:84%
And she said, have
people do whatever

00:27:13.110 --> 00:27:16.540 align:middle line:84%
mindfulness meditation-centering
practice they do.

00:27:16.540 --> 00:27:21.660 align:middle line:10%
And then open themselves to
the creative wisdom of whoever

00:27:21.660 --> 00:27:23.100 align:middle line:10%
inspires them the most.

00:27:23.100 --> 00:27:25.020 align:middle line:10%
So it might be
Leonardo da Vinci.

00:27:25.020 --> 00:27:26.820 align:middle line:90%
It might be Marie Curie.

00:27:26.820 --> 00:27:28.410 align:middle line:90%
It could be Queen Elizabeth I.

00:27:28.410 --> 00:27:30.340 align:middle line:84%
- The collective
consciousness of that.

00:27:30.340 --> 00:27:32.530 align:middle line:10%
- But choose a
particular representation

00:27:32.530 --> 00:27:38.820 align:middle line:10%
that works for you and ask that
it be present with you as you--

00:27:38.820 --> 00:27:39.700 align:middle line:10%
- Pull it down.

00:27:39.700 --> 00:27:41.492 align:middle line:84%
- --pull it down and
approach this problem.

00:27:41.492 --> 00:27:43.057 align:middle line:84%
And it's so simple,
it's so elegant.

00:27:43.057 --> 00:27:43.890 align:middle line:90%
- It's a great idea.

00:27:43.890 --> 00:27:44.690 align:middle line:90%
- Right.

00:27:44.690 --> 00:27:46.440 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:27:46.440 --> 00:27:48.247 align:middle line:84%
- That's how you
generate new ideas.

00:27:48.247 --> 00:27:49.080 align:middle line:90%
- You generate new--

00:27:49.080 --> 00:27:50.080 align:middle line:90%
that's just one of them.

00:27:50.080 --> 00:27:52.500 align:middle line:84%
There's also another great
one from Stephen Russell,

00:27:52.500 --> 00:27:53.640 align:middle line:90%
barefoot doctor.

00:27:53.640 --> 00:27:56.640 align:middle line:10%
And he created this
amazing practice.

00:27:56.640 --> 00:27:58.890 align:middle line:10%
It takes a little too long
to talk about in detail

00:27:58.890 --> 00:28:01.410 align:middle line:10%
now, but you're moving the
energy between the front

00:28:01.410 --> 00:28:04.110 align:middle line:10%
and the back to open up--

00:28:04.110 --> 00:28:07.320 align:middle line:10%
basically, opening up the
crown chakra to let the wisdom

00:28:07.320 --> 00:28:08.308 align:middle line:10%
come powering in.

00:28:08.308 --> 00:28:09.600 align:middle line:90%
- Those two work well together.

00:28:09.600 --> 00:28:10.400 align:middle line:90%
- Yeah.

00:28:10.400 --> 00:28:13.235 align:middle line:84%
So those are the two I put
in for the generation phase

00:28:13.235 --> 00:28:15.360 align:middle line:84%
because they work well
together as you immediately,

00:28:15.360 --> 00:28:16.570 align:middle line:90%
intuitively recognized.

00:28:16.570 --> 00:28:17.370 align:middle line:90%
